<br>
If fear is not allowed, then you need to conserve your mana and try to stay alive till the end.  Melee, and pet classes have an advantage in a free for all, because casters will run oom, and wont be able to finish anyone off at the end, where melees and pet classes will be able to finish people off with their pets and melee abilities.  <br>
<br>
Id play the coward and hide in a fire pot until near the end, try not to attract too much attention to yourself, keep your finger on the heal button to heal yourself, then I'd jump out and finish off whoever is still standing, hehe.  <br>
<br>
People that should be killed first (in order for things to go well for you in the end), warrior, necros, mage, shammy.   Tough call, but my money would be on one of those classes to be the last standing in the format you are describing, because everyone will run oom eventually, and it will come down to who is able to kill without mana. <br>
<br>
